{
  "stem": "25938.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I reminded him of a-- of his people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He let me go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That is what-- what I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Were you-- were you injured by-- by the-- the blows that he did give?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What happened to the other people whose temperatures--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't see them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think they went to the crematories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, the common sense told me that went.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they-- they-- if they took the thermometer, that means that-- it means-- it isn't for nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You looked too pale.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would be happy if I heard that they survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- but I don't think they survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I-- it was a few times, I did it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I sneaked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So people didn't-- didn't think I really-- just-- I didn't do that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember a few times I stayed with a group of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They told me, I didn't have-- didn't any group to go to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You didn't have a group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they-- they could take-- they could take you to crematories.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I stood the group people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they-- and the-- and the SS says, wait.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So people waited, and I didn't wait.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I just went-- ran away, you see?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was how I saved myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you have to be-- see, the reason that you couldn't-- you could not say that I survived because I was-- I was very alert, smart.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But yet, you had to do something for yourself, know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In addition to-- to the fact that people saved my life, I myself saved a few times, like-- like this thing, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a few times, I just sneaked out.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
